                                                  \ /       |       \ /
                                   0.1 (b) -------(a)     (b)      (c)------- (b)  0.1
                                                  /       / | \        \
                                             0.1 /       /  |   \       \ 0.6
                                                /       /   |     \      \
                                              (c)    (a)   (b)    (c)    (c)   
